latestPosts.caption:
Say hello to Match-ed🍵 - A live online matcha workshop with @glow_glossary 💚💚

To the first ever matcha brand that ever bet on me and to every SINGLE MILESTONE we hit together - here’s stacking another one for the books with @pratishtharawat14 @k.avya____ ✨👯‍♀️

This idea has been inspired entirely from my DM’s where I’ve received SO much love and also many long requests of bringing the matcha culture to your city, and while we’re working on an offline plan - we didn’t want to waste anytime in 2025 - so we’re kick starting out FIRST ONLINE WORKSHOP with you! 🍵

latestPosts.caption:
New day, new drop: welcome to my dream matcha bar 🍵🌸
If I ran a café, this rose cardamom matcha would be the bestseller. Luckily, you can make it right from your kitchen and pretend you’re the barista.

The blend🌹
– 3g matcha
– 40ml @thedearist rose water (steam-distilled & edible!)
– 100ml almond milk with cardamom, vanilla & 5g honey

Bowl from @wildflowerceramicist gifted by @naimitaj ❤️❤️

We’ve been whisking this blend over a long time now and we are happy to announce @veronicabahl x Boojee pop up 💚

See you on 6thJune, Boojee 16, 4-7pm!

latestPosts.caption:
ENDLESS SAMPLES LATER, we’re finally here! 🥺🥺

Vero’s blend is officially in production🍵🍵🍵

The matcha is straight from the homeland of matcha, Uji & is everything I wanted it to be. It’s BRIGHT green, very little goes a long way and it has a hint of nutty notes with ZERO bitterness! ☺️

safe to say, a dream that I didn’t even dream of dreaming is coming closer to being my real life. 🥺😭
